Flow Highlights

Lead Finding Agent:

Web search (PubMed, Bard/Gemini) → GPT verification → Hunter.io/email scraping → email validation → Google Sheet.

Lead Emailing Agent:

Filter Status=ready → GPT drafts personalized email → guardrails check → send via Gmail → update Sheet.

Weekly Loop:

Add ~50 leads, send ~50 emails, repeat weekly.
